---
title: Sticky Veggie Udon Noodles and Sweet Chilli Gyozas with Spicy Smacked Cucumber and Crispy Onions
description: Inspired by some of the world's most popular street food, these tasty Sticky Veggie Udon Noodles and Sweet Chilli Gyozas are perfect for a casual sharing-style vegetarian dinner.
